Third-party code
----------------

dynclient/baml-patched/ contains a copied-and-patched fork of the
upstream BAML Go runtime (github.com/boundaryml/baml). That subtree is
licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0; its license text is
preserved verbatim at:

    dynclient/baml-patched/LICENSE

The exact upstream BAML version the subtree was generated from is
recorded at:

    dynclient/baml-patched/BAML_REST_SOURCE_VERSION

Patches applied on top of the upstream source are summarized in:

    dynclient/baml-patched/PATCHES.md
